description: Your cluster's installation is blocked due to ${MSG}. Please review the network configuration, and try re-installing the cluster. Please refer to the product documentation for the firewall prerequisites required for PrivateLink clusters: https://access.redhat.com/documentation/en-us/red_hat_openshift_service_on_aws/4/html/prepare_your_environment/rosa-sts-aws-prereqs#osd-aws-privatelink-firewall-prerequisites_rosa-sts-aws-prereqs#.
